title: Necropoli Orti della Maddalena
description: A Hellenistic and Roman period necropolis located in Messina, Sicily, in the area now referred to as "Orti della Maddalena".

properties.description: Representative location of a Hellenistic and Roman necropolis in the city of Messina, in the area now commonly called "Orti della Maddalena", based on a representative point derived from an OpenStreetMap node.
